s="about-content"><img class="image-5" src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed3ed4f83ac8_ios-close%201.png" width="512" alt="Close Button
" sizes="100vw" data-w-id="6ae67a2f-9aba-5dad-b0d6-4ff8ff589bb1" id="menu-class-name" loading="lazy" srcset="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed3ed4f83ac8_ios-close%25201-p-500.png 500w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed3ed4f83ac8_ios-close%25201-p-800.png 800w, https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed3ed4f83ac8_ios-close%201.png 1024w"/><h1 class="h1 about">About Shambapro</h1><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed6d5af83ac5_heylagostechie-IgUR1iX0mqM-unsplash.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="About Image" class="about-image"/><p class="paragraph about">Shambapro is a next-generation agtech startup that helps farmers in Africa to build and run profitable sustainable farm businesses. <br/><br/>We are based in Kigali, Rwanda. <br/><br/>Shambapro enables small scale farmers in Africa access suitable agriculture financing without traditional collateral and other value chain services like ready and better markets, quality affordable inputs, agriculture extension services and technical support etc. <br/><br/>Small Scale Farmers can access the platform by downloading the Shambapro App, simple-to-use Farm Management tool from Google Playstore or Appstore.<br/><br/>Farmers can use the Shambapro App to maintain production and financial records, manage their farm store or inventory, set task, supervise and approve tasks done by farm workers,  and generate instant financial and production reports. <br/><br/>Shambapro works with interested business partners to provide unique dashboards that help them to serve farmers better. Such partners include produce buyers or off takers, out-grower programs, farm input suppliers, farm service providers, and banks and other lenders and Non-Governmental Organizations. <br/><br/>Permission to access farmer data is only given by the farmer themselves who fullyown their own data. <br/><br/>Shambapro was founded in 2018 by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kelvinodoobo/" target="_blank" class="link-text bold-text"><span>Kelvin Odoobo</span></a>, after over fifteen (15) years of working with small scale farmers in Africa and regularly facing the frustrations and day to day challenges that they face as they try to actualize their dreams of creating profitable and sustainable farm businesses.<br/>‍<br/>For inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@shambapro.com" class="link-text bold-text"><span class="link-text bold-text">hello@shambapro.com</span></a> <br/></p><a href="mailto:hello@shambapro.com" class="button contact-sidebar w-button">Contact Us</a></div></div><div id="about-section" style="display:none;opacity:0;-webkit-transform:translate3d(492px, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(492px, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(492px, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(492px, 0, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0)" class="navlinkssidebar"><div id="w-node-_2cc91a55-2cf7-71e0-d332-f3f1b695333f-23f83a9d" class="link-sidebar-wrapper"><img class="image-5" src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed3ed4f83ac8_ios-close%201.png" width="512" alt="Close Button
