st-child w-inline-block"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed469df83aa6_app-store%201.svg" alt="App Store Logo"/><div class="text-block">App Store</div></a></div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed927bf83aea_Group%2020.svg" style="opacity:0" data-w-id="96ae1cb9-e9dc-2f53-c301-cd57f4e5a3b0" alt="Blob" class="headimg"/><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed1452f83aec_Group%2028.svg" style="opacity:0" data-w-id="f3acd0e0-7691-01d6-8958-ebb03e911692" alt="Blob" class="headimg _2"/><div class="form-wrapper top"><div data-w-id="38537c4f-35b9-c9ea-519d-8a1e6d062e0c" style="opacity:0" class="form-block w-form"><form id="email-form" name="email-form" data-name="Email Form" action="https://shambapro.us1.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=142832d078c22c93b62626a6c&amp;amp;id=152ab124cf" method="post" class="form"><input type="email" class="text-field w-input" maxlength="256" name="EMAIL" data-name="EMAIL" placeholder="Email address" id="EMAIL-5" required=""/><input type="submit" value="Request Early Access" data-wait="Please wait..." class="button w-button"/></form><div class="w-form-done"><div>Thank you! Your submission has been received!</div></div><div class="w-form-fail"><div>Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form.</div></div></div></div></div><div id="w-node-d013de4c-53c9-a013-0e79-df301868b55f-23f83a9d" class="div-block-4"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49edc461f83ae5_7.png" loading="lazy" alt="" class="feature-image top"/></div></div></div><div class="form-wrapper bottom"><div class="paragraph bottom">Request for Early Access</div><div data-w-id="58f50844-63b1-44f9-d4f6-f2ab1fba45ae" style="opacity:0" class="form-block w-form"><form id="email-form" name="email-form" data-name="Email Form" action="https://shambapro.us1.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=142832d078c22c93b62626a6c&amp;amp;id=152ab124cf" method="get" class="form"><input type="email" class="text-field w-input" maxlength="256" name="EMAIL" data-name="EMAIL" placeholder="Email address" id="EMAIL-4" required=""/><input type="submit" value="Request Early Access" data-wait="Please wait..." class="button w-button"/></form><div class="w-form-done"><div>Thank you! Your submission has been received!</div></div><div class="w-form-fail"><div>Oops! Something went wrong while submitting the form.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="section intro hide wf-section"><div class="wrapper"><div class="w-layout-grid _2-col-img-grid"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed2dbdf83abd_607f246abd32f34f5871cdf0_section2.png" data-w-id="0d0aa15a-7abf-de2a-8290-fb8c31c73c15" alt="Splash Screen " class="feature-image section-2"/><div data-w-id="0d0aa15a-7abf-de2a-8290-fb8c31c73c16" class="feature-dec right"><p class="paragraph hide">Over the past decade, the banking and financial services industry in Ghana has seen significant improvements in the quality of service delivery and the provision of superior financial products and packages.</p><h3 class="h3 section2">We enable remote access to farm owners and investors to view and monitor all farm activities and financial transactions conducted by the farm manager, farm experts (e.g. agronomists, veterinary doctors etc) and farm workers, all in one place.</h3></div></div></div></div><div id="how" data-w-id="aa3c8025-f0d6-6c3f-0998-1d589561d642" class="section wf-section"><div class="wrapper"><div data-w-id="aa3c8025-f0d6-6c3f-0998-1d589561d644" style="opacity:0" class="heading-center"><h1 data-w-id="aa3c8025-f0d6-6c3f-0998-1d589561d647" class="h1 short"><strong class="bold-text">An all-in-one <br/></strong></h1><h1 data-w-id="50770724-56e6-dffc-b06c-f6ed1b218578" class="h1 short"><strong class="bold-text">Farm Management Tool</strong></h1></div><div class="w-layout-grid _2-col-img-grid ft head"><div data-w-id="aa3c8025-f0d6-6c3f-0998-1d589561d64a" class="feature-dec left"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed10cbf83aeb_Group%2023.svg" alt="wifi" class="ft-icon hide"/><p class="paragraph"><strong class="bold-text-2">Many farmers fail in their farm businesses because they often do not have control of what happens on their farms. Also, they do not keep accurate records and cannot demonstrate the profitability of their farm business to lenders, partners, investors or supporters.<br/>‍<br/>‍</strong><strong>Farm Calendar</strong><strong class="bold-text-2"> helps you schedule, allocate and approve farm tasks as well as measure the level of satisfaction of the performed task. <br/><br/></strong><strong>Production Records</strong><strong class="bold-text-2"> enables you to keep different types of non-financial farm records e.g. feeding, breeding, milking or health records. You can also track records of a specific animal, herd , flock, crop field or paddock.<br/><br/>‍</strong><strong>Financial Records</strong><strong class="bold-text-2"> empowers you to keep track of the farm’s finances, to ensure integrity, transparency and accuracy.<br/>‍<br/>‍</strong><strong>Farm Store</strong><strong class="bold-text-2"> lets you manage your stock including farm produce, farm inputs, livestock and have first hand information on what gets in or out in real time.<br/><br/>With </strong><strong>Farm Team</strong><strong class="bold-text-2">, you can invite and collaborate with farm workers, farm experts like agronomists and veterinary doctors, in managing your farm. <br/><br/>‍</strong><strong>Farm Reports</strong><strong class="bold-text-2"> allows you to check the financial health of your farm at any time. You can also generate enterprise reports, breeding reports, production reports and labour reports etc.<br/>‍</strong><strong>‍<br/></strong>Small scale farmers can use <strong>Shambapro Basic</strong> for <strong>FREE</strong> while more commercial farmers or farms can access advanced features in <strong>Shambapro Plus </strong>and <strong>Shambapro Enterprise</strong> (Coming Soon).<strong><br/><br/>For more info about the Shambapro App, go to </strong><span data-w-id="4620c519-9b5d-0461-9d59-3f6b5ab19ac2" class="link-text"><strong class="bold-text-2">About Shambapro</strong></span><strong class="bold-text-2">.</strong><br/></p></div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ede05df83ae4_4.png" data-w-id="aa3c8025-f0d6-6c3f-0998-1d589561d652" id="w-node-aa3c8025-f0d6-6c3f-0998-1d589561d652-23f83a9d" alt="create a task screen" class="feature-image right d"/></div></div></div><div id="partner" class="wf-section"><div class="wrapper"><div data-w-id="d5477f08-0c17-7de2-7e1f-4a8fbb13b271" style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 55PX, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 55PX, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 55PX, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 55PX, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0" class="title-wrap"><h1 class="partner_header-text">Partner with Us</h1><p class="paragraph-large">Shambapro Digital Agriculture Platform enables small scale farmers in Africa to access suitable agriculture financing and other value chain services. <br/><br/>We are building an ecosystem to help solve challenges and reduce the real and perceive risk around the small scale farmer. <br/><br/>We love to talk to companies and organisations whose mission and values are similar to ours to explore opportunities for collaboration through our Shambapro Business and Shambapro Partner programs</p></div><div data-w-id="7c4e518f-4a53-129d-7b25-aa755eb246d3" style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 55PX, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 55PX, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 55PX, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 55PX, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);opacity:0" class="w-layout-grid feature-grid"><a href="https://4350vqir2v0.typeform.com/to/M7QUuWYQ" class="feature-card w-inline-block"><div class="div-block-9"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed0b01f83ada_9.png" loading="lazy" alt="" class="icon"/><h4 class="partner-card_header">Shambapro Business</h4><p class="partner-card_para"><strong>Shambapro Business</strong> engages, vets, creates and maintains partnerships with interested farm input suppliers, service Providers and financial service providers in countries where it is active.</p></div><div href="#beta" data-w-id="feecd14c-4cd0-f05e-75cc-8f4768ba7fde" style="opacity:0" class="button-icon button is--partner"><div class="text-block"><strong>Join Shambapro Business</strong></div></div></a><a href="https://4350vqir2v0.typeform.com/to/FLlCiBpy" class="feature-card w-inline-block"><div class="div-block-9"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed2ff5f83adb_8.png" loading="lazy" alt="" class="icon"/><h4 class="partner-card_header">Shambapro Partner</h4><p class="partner-card_para"><strong>Shambapro Partner</strong> engages and explores opportunities of collaborations with interested not-for-profit organisations that seek to empower farmers to increase yields, quality and farm incomes sustainably across Africa.</p></div><div href="#beta" data-w-id="dcee3a62-e63e-1688-6e9d-be9d93d31225" style="opacity:0" class="button-icon button is--partner"><div class="text-block"><strong class="bold-text-3">Become a Shambapro Partner </strong></div></div></a></div></div></div><div data-w-id="524c5762-40af-5cd4-7638-f0c2679d10c1" class="section bg-diff hide wf-section"><div class="wrapper"><div class="w-layout-grid _2-col-img-grid ft"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49edac46f83abe_4.png" data-w-id="1b16229c-9167-1feb-ac92-59b76cb44262" alt="Record Transaction" class="feature-image right b"/><div id="w-node-_9fa00e44-f071-b7d1-9aae-625306e206d8-23f83a9d" data-w-id="9fa00e44-f071-b7d1-9aae-625306e206d8" class="feature-dec right"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ede9b1f83ae7_Group%2024.svg" alt="Shield" class="ft-icon hide"/><h3 class="h3"><strong>Control Your Farm’s Finances</strong></h3><p class="paragraph">Many farmers fail in their farm businesses because they often do not have control of how cash flows in our out of their businesses. <strong>Farm Records</strong> gives you to the tools to control and monitor your farm’s financial transactions and to ensure integrity in how the farm’s financial records are made and maintained. </p></div></div></div></div><div data-w-id="5abdf430-afe2-454c-c787-737dbccde98a" class="section et hide wf-section"><div class="wrapper"><div class="w-layout-grid _2-col-img-grid ft"><div data-w-id="5abdf430-afe2-454c-c787-737dbccde993" class="feature-dec left"><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49ed10cbf83aeb_Group%2023.svg" alt="Wifi" class="ft-icon hide"/><h3 class="h3"><strong>Make Data-Driven Farm Business Decisions</strong></h3><p class="paragraph">Generate instant <strong>Farm Reports</strong> and Analytics to he help you and your team make informed farm decisions based  on farm and remote data to enable you increase quality and quantity of yields and improved farm productivity.<br/></p></div><img src="https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/60dc28801e49eddb76f83a9c/60dc28801e49eda1b8f83abc_5.png" data-w-id="5abdf430-afe2-454c-c787-737dbccde99b" alt="Report Screen" class="feature-image right d"/></div></div></div><div class="logo-section"><div data-w-id="e8b170d0-d5d3-4bbe-45e1-1f6db94def59" style="-webkit